titocc.compiler.types

Class PointerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • titocc.compiler.types.CType
      • titocc.compiler.types.PointerType

  • public class PointerType
extends CType
    Corresponds to C pointer type. Is an object and a scalar, but not arithmetic. Equals only to PointerType that has same pointed type.
